troublemaking offspring...

13:24.985 --> 13:27.254
Would upset the balance.

13:29.057 --> 13:30.793
I need you to bring her
back to me.

13:32.126 --> 13:35.863
Your original offer
was one million pounds.

13:35.929 --> 13:37.565
Well, now it's two...

13:39.000 --> 13:40.601
'Cause you are
the right fit for this.

13:41.035 --> 13:42.503
I can see that.

13:43.270 --> 13:44.705
How do you know
she's even in there?

13:46.274 --> 13:48.210
It is the only place
she would go.

13:52.313 --> 13:53.314
Hmm.

13:54.115 --> 13:55.716
That will get you into the zone.

13:55.817 --> 13:57.851
And whatever else you need
whilst you're there

13:57.918 --> 13:59.420
will be provided for you.

14:01.722 --> 14:05.560
And when you get there,
find Jane.

14:06.628 --> 14:09.097
Who's Jane?

14:09.230 --> 14:12.067
Jane might be my best creation.

14:12.333 --> 14:17.472
Problematic at times,
but, oh, so unique.

14:19.407 --> 14:22.043
Melissa was always
so fond of her.

14:22.143 --> 14:26.148
I would start your search there.

14:29.951 --> 14:31.253
Hmm.

14:35.190 --> 14:37.659
<i>Well, hello, Jane.</i>

14:39.027 --> 14:40.796
<i>How are you feeling?</i>

14:41.830 --> 14:43.865
<i>Are you feeling fine?</i>

14:51.239 --> 14:55.244
<i>I wanted to see
what you're made of, Jane.</i>

14:56.277 --> 14:57.913
<i>I would die for you.</i>

14:59.413 --> 15:01.884
<i>I'm gonna make you die for me.</i>

15:04.251 --> 15:08.156
<i>I'm gonna have to hurt you bad.</i>

