Tell me again.

17:38.772 --> 17:40.841
I love you.

17:53.186 --> 17:55.956
No, not this one.

17:58.192 --> 17:59.428
Understood.

18:00.260 --> 18:01.462
Follow me.

18:19.547 --> 18:23.985
If you would like a man,
all you need to do is ask.

18:26.020 --> 18:32.426
What you choose here
remains absolutely confidential.

