20:33.080 --> 20:35.983
All I want is
to feel something real.

20:37.984 --> 20:40.754
But I can't control that.
Only you can.

20:42.789 --> 20:46.961
I do what you want.
You make this real.

20:49.230 --> 20:50.899
I want to see more of you.

20:52.066 --> 20:53.201
