20:55.670 --> 20:57.205
Unbutton your shirt.

21:17.490 --> 21:18.894
Stop, stop.

21:20.996 --> 21:22.030
Leave it there.

21:23.265 --> 21:24.566
Just like that.

21:57.664 --> 21:59.166
