22:35.603 --> 22:37.772
On the joint, I could taste her.

22:37.872 --> 22:39.274
Mm-hmm.

22:42.609 --> 22:44.044
You didn't taste her.

22:44.612 --> 22:46.013
You tasted me.

22:54.688 --> 22:57.225
I never told anyone I saw you.

22:58.259 --> 22:59.827
I know.

23:04.932 --> 23:06.701
So I'm a... I'm a good boy.

23:06.934 --> 23:10.503
Yeah, you were.
You kept our secret.

23:10.570 --> 23:11.939
Yeah.

23:20.682 --> 23:22.049
Yes.

