26:20.728 --> 26:22.130
<i>Good evening, David.</i>

26:22.696 --> 26:23.997
<i>Welcome to the zone.</i>

27:50.218 --> 27:52.019
I met a man tonight.

27:52.720 --> 27:54.020
I can make him want me.

27:54.422 --> 27:59.460
<i>Yes, you speak
of client 389, Mr. Russell.</i>

27:59.727 --> 28:02.163
Mm-hmm. I can...

28:02.229 --> 28:06.467
<i>He has requested never
to be matched with you again.</i>

28:18.246 --> 28:19.246
Why?

28:19.480 --> 28:22.750
<i>He was completely
satisfied with your encounter.</i>

28:23.183 --> 28:26.186
<i>He did not want to ruin
the memory of it.</i>

28:27.555 --> 28:28.555
<i>You did well.</i>

28:34.295 --> 28:36.663
I want to put a shotgun
in my mouth

28:36.730 --> 28:38.031
and pull the trigger.

28:40.934 --> 28:43.637
Was I programmed
to feel that way?

28:44.571 --> 28:46.573
Despair, yes.

28:47.375 --> 28:51.244
Powerful men are very attracted
to those who suffer,

28:51.645 --> 28:52.812
to the helpless.

28:53.647 --> 28:58.019
Client 389, Mr. Russell,
will speak with his friends.

28:58.419 --> 29:02.256
They will request you.
You will do well with them.

29:10.163 --> 29:11.566
There's something else.

29:16.170 --> 29:18.538
Someone has been
sending me messages.

29:20.074 --> 29:21.676
What kind of messages?

29:22.109 --> 29:23.443
Voice messages.

29:24.444 --> 29:27.781
The voice is distorted,
but it's a man's voice.

29:29.982 --> 29:31.551
He doesn't tell me his name.

29:32.752 --> 29:34.087
What does he say?

29:34.954 --> 29:36.656
That he's going to kill me.

29:38.526 --> 29:40.728
And you believe
that you are afraid.

29:41.994 --> 29:43.663
Yes, I believe I'm afraid.

29:43.897 --> 29:45.264
I will review these messages.

29:45.332 --> 29:49.704
I am certain
there is a simple explanation.

29:49.804 --> 29:51.371
Yes, someone wants to kill me.

29:51.471 --> 29:54.775
Or someone is paying
for the ability

29:54.842 --> 29:56.910
to make you believe that.

29:57.443 --> 30:01.682
You were created
to serve the clients, Jane.

30:02.048 --> 30:04.617
If a client wants
to threaten you,

30:04.884 --> 30:08.489
I am certain
he is paying to do so.

30:09.557 --> 30:12.293
