Hey, you Jane? I'm David.

35:13.460 --> 35:15.596
I'm looking for Melissa veidt.
Her father sent me.

35:16.028 --> 35:17.063
Melissa?

35:17.364 --> 35:18.965
Yeah. Can I come in?

35:41.521 --> 35:44.190
- What happened to Melissa?
- I don't know.

35:44.690 --> 35:46.793
That's what her father
sent me here to find out.

35:51.164 --> 35:52.932
You look uncomfortable, David.

35:56.336 --> 35:57.737
Well, you have an apartment.

35:58.371 --> 35:59.639
I do.

36:00.340 --> 36:02.108
Why does a machine
need an apartment?

36:03.342 --> 36:05.812
